casebody.head_matter:
Tracy NIXON, petitioner,
v.
Greg ABBOTT, Attorney General of Texas, et al.
No. 13-8590.
Supreme Court of the United States
April 21, 2014.
Case below, 2013 WL 4781535.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Texas, Fifth District, dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
